        <mxCell id="22" value="Each Order aggregates&lt;br/&gt;multiple Samples (→ State 5.3).&lt;br/&gt;All Samples must reach&lt;br/&gt;SampleStatus.Completed (3)&lt;br/&gt;before this transition fires.&lt;br/&gt;There is no explicit SP that&lt;br/&gt;transitions Order Status 1→2;&lt;br/&gt;it is set programmatically via&lt;br/&gt;UpdateOrderAsync / sp_UpdateOrder." style="shape=note;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;backgroundOutline=1;size=12;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#000000;strokeWidth=1;fontSize=8;align=left;spacingLeft=8;spacingTop=6;spacingRight=6;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" parent="1">
